Description_lang: Summons Aegira, who fights by your side for $d and imbues you with $n charges of Odyn's Wrath.  Attacking causes you to consume a charge, dealing an additional $210937s1 Nature damage.  Once all charges of Odyn's Wrath are consumed, your target takes an additional $211316s1 Nature damage.
AuraDescription_lang: Occasionally call down the power of Odyn, causing lightning to hit the target for $210937s1 Nature damage.
